#########
# Point #
#########

@Node Point "What is Point & Rock"

Point & Rock is "Yet Another DiscMag" about  music. But it will speak
about  Hard  Rock and  only Hard  Rock. I will  try  to provide you a
complete  information  on this subject, but as other discmags, I need
@{b}YOU@{ub}.

You can easily understand that the creation of a magazine is a lot of
work. So  if  you  want something  quite regular, you need some help.
This is where you can act.

Go on to the @{"Contribution" Link Contribution} section to check out what you can do.

@{b}Why this mag ?@{ub}

Music is  my  passion as well as  my Amiga. So, why not link together
these two passions and share it with all the community ?
Another fact  is that  I have not already seen this kind of Hard Rock
mag around the Aminet.
Third reason, I'm a belgian and it seems that the belgian Amiga Users
are not so productives  so I want  to contribute to fill this hole in
Amiga  Scene ( come  on  you  my  compatriots, let's  show'em   we're 
alive !!! )

Well, Point  & Rock  is born. Let's  see now how far it will go ! But
please let me know your impressions ( crap, mean, good, excellent ? )
just to improve the quality.

I don't know yet the  frequency of this mag, but I think that every 2
months is not a bad thing. Maybe  every  month (?). It will depend of
my studies and of you !!!

That's it for this editorial. 

Enjoy Point & Rock 1



                                         Raphaël ^ Mister No/aßS

@Endnode

