@Node Final "Final Words"

You  finaly  reached  the  end  of  issue  #1  of  Point & Rock. This
experiment has been a pleasure for me. The ball  is now on your side.
I really hope you will catch it and send it back to me.

I need  you  to  continue. So  don't hesitate to send me whatever you
want :  adverts, concert  reports, album  tests, letter... Everything
will be used.
I wait your stuff, you Metallibashers, Irons and others.

Hard  Rock  is  a good  kind of  music. It provides us the power, the
key to express all the madness inside of us. But it  also can give us
the melody to let our  heart  explode ( nice sentence he ? ). Come on
tell me why you listen to this music, how you discovered it and since
when.

I give you a rendez-vous to the next edition of Point & Rock.

But  don't  forget : "Play  it  loud, don't  play  it  low, blow your
speakers with ROCK N ROLL" ( Manowar ).





                                Yours, 
                                Mister No ^ aßS


