####################
# Albums to listen #
####################

@Node Albums "Albums to listen"

@{b}WHITE ZOMBIE : Super Sexy Swinging Sounds@{ub}

This  CD  is an  album of remixes. The group has decided to  give the
bands  of Astro  Creep 2000 ( their last album ) to some DJ's in hope
to create other songs.
Some other  bands have already tried this. I think to @{"Metallica" Link Metallica} with
the single "Until it sleeps". Moby worked on  it one night to produce
a completely  revamped  song  and  I must say that  the  attempt is a
success.
White Zombie's case is other. Don't  expect  too much different songs
on this album. The order  of the songs changes  from Astro Creep 2000
but the vocal parts  are quite  the same. It's just  the beat  or the
arrangement  that are  different ( you  can  hear  some jungle beats,
dance, techno and so on ).
In fact, I can't say that this album is  bad 'coz the songs are quite
nice but  the principle  of the  remix is the  change  completely the
song and this is not really the case of this album.

@{u}The conclusion@{uu} : if you are open-minded, you  could perhaps listen to
Super Sexy Swinging Sounds, but  if  you're an  unconditional  fan of
pure Heavy, this is not for you !

My Quote : 6.5/10

@endnode


