and it  prefigures a best  of ( out on the 23rd of september ) called
" Best of The Beast ".
The single  is available  in  three  different  formats : 
- CD1 : Virus + My Generation + Doctor, doctor
- CD2 : Virus + Sanctuary + Wrathchild
- LP 12" : Virus + Invasion + Prowler + poster bag

@{b}Van Halen@{ub}

Sammy  Haggar is  fired  and  replaced  by... David  Lee  Roth ! They
actualy are working on a best of and maybe a  tour is planned for the
next year !?
 
